From: "Aneesh Kumar K.V" <aneesh.kumar@linux.vnet.ibm.com>

vfs: Add BUG_ON for delayed and unwritten flags in submit_bh

The BH_Delay and BH_Unwritten flags should never leak out to
submit_bh().  If this happens flag a BUG so we can get a stack trace
and determine how and why this happened.

(n.b.: Only XFS and ext4 use these buffer head flags currently.)

Signed-off-by: Aneesh Kumar K.V <aneesh.kumar@linux.vnet.ibm.com>
Signed-off-by: "Theodore Ts'o" <tytso@mit.edu>
Cc: xfs@oss.sgi.com
